RACE.RACE_TEXT: Dr. Glenn Blodgett S. LONE STAR PARK RACE 9 350 Y Dirt CR: 98. Stakes Purse 56500. FOR ACCREDITED TEXAS-BRED THREE YEAR OLDS AND UPWARD. No nomination fee. $500 to pass the entry box and an additional $500 to start. Supplemental Nomination of $2,000 is due at the time of entry and includes all fees. The $50,000 added and all fees to be divided 55% to the owner of the winner, 17% to second, $10% to third, $5% to fourth, $3% to fifth and 2% for placing sixth through tenth. If less than ten horses start, the purse monies not distributed will revert to the winning owner. Weights: Thre e Year Olds, 125 lbs., Older 128 lbs. Total earnings in 2022-2023 as determined by the information provided by Equibase Company will be used in determining preference of horses. Starters to be named through the entry box by the usual time of closing. Th e field will be limited to ten starters. Horses not drawing a starting position in the gate will receive a refund of the entry fee. A trophy will be presented to the winning owner.
